@Mock(lenient = true) was introduced in `Mockito` version `2.23.3`.

You either have to upgrade or use the [`other way`][1] to write this:

```java
lenient().given(specialtyRepository.save(argThat(argument -&gt; argument.getDescription().equals(MATCH_ME)))).willReturn(savedSpeciality);
```




[1]: https://static.javadoc.io/org.mockito/mockito-core/2.23.0/org/mockito/Mockito.html#mockito_lenient

